        {"english": "Success starts with self-belief.", "japanese": "成功は自信から始まります。", "romaji": "Seikou wa jishin kara hajimarimasu."},
        {"english": "Every moment is a fresh start.", "japanese": "すべての瞬間が新しい出発です。", "romaji": "Subete no shunkan ga atarashii shuppatsu desu."},
        {"english": "Don't wait for opportunity, create it.", "japanese": "チャンスを待たずに、作り出しましょう。", "romaji": "Chansu o matazu ni, tsukuridashimashou."},
        {"english": "Wake up with determination.", "japanese": "決意を持って目覚めましょう。", "romaji": "Ketsui o motte mezamemashou."},
        {"english": "Your potential is endless.", "japanese": "あなたの可能性は無限です。", "romaji": "Anata no kanousei wa mugen desu."},
        {"english": "Keep moving forward.", "japanese": "前に進み続けましょう。", "romaji": "Mae ni susumi tsudukemashou."},
