        {"english": "You've got this, keep going.", "japanese": "あなたならできる、続けてください。", "romaji": "Anata nara dekiru, tsuzukete kudasai."},
        {"english": "Small progress is still progress.", "japanese": "小さな進歩も進歩です。", "romaji": "Chiisana shinpo mo shinpo desu."},
